<section title="Overview">
<abstract>
<i>Metaphysical Positivism</i> is systematic constructive positivist philosophy.
We present here sketches of <i>Metaphysical Positivism</i> together with some related historical material which might possibly help the reader come to an understanding of this system and its place in the history of ideas.
</abstract>
